RIX_SLIST_NEXT(elm, base, field)

Modifiers

RIX_SLIST_INSERT_HEAD(head, base, elm, field)

RIX_SLIST_INSERT_AFTER(base, slistelm, elm, field)

RIX_SLIST_REMOVE_HEAD(head, base, field)

RIX_SLIST_REMOVE_AFTER(base, elm, field)

